NA</td><td>NA</td><td>&plus;</td><td>NA</td><td>Y165 contact (RIN4); position AvrB R266</td></tr><tr><td>ADP pocket</td><td>N62A</td><td>&plusmn;</td><td>&plusmn;</td><td>NA</td><td>NA</td><td>&plus;</td><td>NA</td><td>Purine ring</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Y65A</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&minus;</td><td>NA</td><td>NA</td><td>&plus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>Purine ring, ribose O<sub>2</sub> H-bond</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>R99A</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>NA</td><td>&plus;</td><td>&alpha;-Phosphate H-bond</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>F113A</td><td>&plusmn;</td><td>&plusmn;</td><td>NA</td><td>NA</td><td>&plus;</td><td>NA</td><td>Phosphate contact; position AvrB R99 and R266</td></tr><tr><td>Interlobe</td><td>Y131A</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>&beta;-Phosphate (via H<sub>2</sub>O)</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>D297A</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&minus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>&plus;</td><td>Purine ring, ribose O<sub>3</sub> (via H<sub>2</sub>O)</td></tr></tbody></table> --><!-- <table-wrap-foot><fn id="nt101"><p><sup>a</sup>Contacts both RIN4<sub>142&ndash;176</sub> or ADP in the crystal structures.</p></fn><fn id="nt102"><p>NA, not attempted.</p></fn></table-wrap-foot> --></table-wrap><p>The authors regret these errors and thank K. Caldwell and R. Michelmore for alerting us to them.</p></sec></body></article>